{
  "stem": "10353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I was ready to go in to the quarters of this compound, I saw three-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] three huge trucks came in and gendarmes and Arrow Cross guys were surrounding this company.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I took off right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't go into the quarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I start running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But where do you run?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember getting onto the street car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as I got onto the street car, on the platform, as I walked in, I was in front right of two Germans and two Arrow Cross guys, right on the platform.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, what do I do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If I get off, they'll know there is something wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If I go and sit down, they'll detect me that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I just stood beside them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went two stations and I got off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And by that time, I had some inkling that there is an orphanage-- it's called the Columbus Orphanage- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and that they are protected by the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But to get in there was very difficult, because it was also guarded by the Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "By that time, Budapest was bombed very, very heavily and the area was-- a great part of the area was demolished.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I tried to circle around that area and to see where I can find one house where I can go over the fence or under the fence.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And luckily, I found one house that had a huge crater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I slipped into the orphanage there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now there, I was several days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I wasn't the only one that was so smart, because people in the city found out about this orphanage and they stared to flock in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Was it an orphanage for children?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was originally meant an orphanage for children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was supposedly run by the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this orphanage, I found a cousin-- a daughter of one of my first cousins, who was really an orphan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was-- when she saw me, she was flabbergasted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she says she knows a source that she can give me documents that I shouldn't stay here, because, you know, this is going to be raided.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was supposed to give me the documents on a Saturday evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I come to see her, she says she's very sorry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She couldn't get the documents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She got me one document, a false document.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She couldn't get me any more and she doesn't know when.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I saw what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By that time, hundreds and hundreds of people came in there, try to find refuge.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the morning, I decided that I have to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was-- with this one document, I was just on my way to the washroom area-- I tried to shave, I shouldn't look like a real refugee or one of the guys from the brigade-- when all of a sudden, again, a whole bunch of trucks came in.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Gendarmes and soldiers and Arrow Cross people surrounded the whole outfit, the whole orphanage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were shouting, shouting that everybody should line up and line up and line up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they chased everybody with the rifle butts and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had to line up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they started to march us-- there was a small football field where they marched us out and they lined us up there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Hundreds of people by that time were in that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was multi-story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was multi-story building.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they announced, anybody that has a Swedish citizenship paper or Swiss citizenship papers should come forward and show the papers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We thought that this was it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we ran and we presented the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They took the papers and then they told us to go back into the line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they confiscated the papers and they lined us up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then they started to sort of segregate people by age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they lined us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And again, under heavy, heavy guards with the gendarmes and this Arrow Cross, they marched us to a building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was called Teleki Square, T-E-L-E-K-I Square.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was a multi-story building and they marched us in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this was on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "On Monday morning, I was-- this time I was very unlucky, because they put me on the third floor and some people were on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On Monday morning, Wallenberg came with a bus and demanded that all the Swedish-- all the people there with Swedish papers should be released.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But people didn't have anymore the Swedish papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But nonetheless, they broke open by force the portals and they jammed into the bus, so anybody that was on the ground floor got first shot.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
